beer_brewer_name: Magners GB / Shepton Mallet Cider Mill (C&C; Group)
review_blob: I come from Cider country in SW England, and I can tell you this is a great Cider. Sweet Ciders are terrible and people dont drink very much of them. The Dry Ciders are the best, and Blackthorn " Rocket Fuel" is one of the bigger and better names. There are more and more Ciders on the market, but most are only available in the UK.
